closing_comment: The standard is to just put the name of the station, not 'ABC MRT station'. Same logic as bus stop. Is 'XYZ' and not 'XYZ bus stop'  I‚Äôm assuming you are using Nominatim, the search function on OpenStreetMaps. Nominatim is designed primarily for finding individual locations by name or address, not listing all POIs of a given type in an area. It is just one of many different searches that can use osm data, each has their advantage/disadvantage  It offers a layer=railway filter, which allows matching of railway infrastructure (such as railways), but very few stations are indexed in its database‚Äîso results may be incomplete even if you use the correct filters  Best Approach: Use the Overpass API  Overpass Turbo Wizard (beginner option)  Go to overpass-turbo.eu, open the Wizard, and enter: railway=station in Singapore  It will translate into a full Overpass QL query and show all nodes/ways tagged railway=station within Singapore.

Established by Kristina Pakhomova, an alumna of Lasalle University Singapore, KrisP Production leverages the power of theater and film production methods to foster not simply artistic talent but also to boost interpersonal communications, increase self-confidence, and help with team-building efforts.  At its core, KrisP Production is dedicated to redefining the borders of typical acting classes. By integrating methodologies such as the Michael Chekhov Technique, Meisner Technique, Viewpoints, and Acting on Camera into its curriculum, KrisP gives an abundant and varied knowing environment suited for specialist and ambitious actors alike. Nonetheless, what truly sets KrisP apart is its commitment to using these very same artistic concepts to the corporate sphere.  Recognizing the parallels between effective acting and effective business communication, KrisP Production offers customized workshops focused on improving public speaking, presentation abilities, and social interactions within expert setups. These workshops are diligently created for corporate customers, international schools, government organizations, and individuals seeking to boost their specialist persona via authenticity and psychological intelligence.  KrisP's corporate training programs are not mere lecture sessions; they are interactive, experiential workshops that urge individuals to step out of their comfort areas.

There seems to be a big problem in this border area with using names not as names, but as tagging for the renderer, and also not actually setting the meta-data that should really be used for the information. Naming a causeway 'Causeway' is also wrong.  Either it has a full name, or it should not be named at all.
